'''Trifaraleen gas''' was a [[Poison/Legends|poisonous]] gas that was used by [[IG-88B|IG-88]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It formed a cloud around the target, choked them, and would finally turn them to dust. Trifaraleen was [[Acid/Legends|acidic]] and could chew through metal. Despite its effectiveness, trifaraleen dissipated quickly outside containment or a host.

==Appearances==
